text: Stanley Moore (18 April 1886 - 22 March 1948) was an Australian cricketer. He played eight first-class matches for New South Wales and Queensland between 1912/13 and 1920/21. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1886 births Category:1948 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Queensland cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
